title: What.the.Bleep.Extended.Quantum.Rabbit.Hole.Edition
description:
What the BLEEP?! The 5 hour Quantum Rabbit Hole Edition
-------------------------------------------------------

Personally I found this film changed my life when I first saw it almost
10 years ago and it continues to have a palpable positive effect in the
way I perceive my reality.

Other people seem to this it's horse shit so whatever - take it or leave
it!!

This torrent includes:

* Disc 1 and Disc 2 of the Quantum Rabbit Hole Edition
* The original theatrical version
* All 20 interviews from Disc 4 and Disc 5

All discs ripped with MakeMKV and converted to mp4 with ffmpeg:

Video...........: x264 CRF 22
Profile.........: High
Level...........: 4
Audio...........: aac 192k

The video quality of the files is not an indication of a defect in my
encoding process. The original DVD quality is just poor. It looks
identical when playing straight from the DVD.

Constructive criticism welcome (Trolls, don't bother coming out from
under your bridge)
